<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">

<head>

    <meta charset="UTF-8">

    <title>Mini Tour กำแพงเพชร</title>

    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+Thai:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans Thai', sans-serif;
            background: #f5f7fb;
        }

        header {

            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f4c81, #1f8dd6);

            color: white;

            padding: 30px;

            text-align: center;

            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, .15);

        }

        header h1 {

            margin: 0;

            font-size: 34px;

        }

        header p {

            opacity: .9;

            font-size: 17px;

        }

        .container {

            width: 92%;

            margin: auto;

            margin-top: 25px;

        }

        .card {

            background: white;

            border-radius: 20px;

            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, .1);

            padding: 15px;

        }

        footer {

            text-align: center;

            padding: 20px;

            color: #666;

        }
    </style>

</head>

<body>

    <header>

        <h1>Mini Tour กำแพงเพชร</h1>

        <p>One Day Trip พร้อมแผนที่สถานที่ท่องเที่ยว</p>

    </header>

    <div class="container">

        <div class="card">

            {{ map|safe }}

        </div>

    </div>

    <footer>

        Mini Tour Kamphaeng Phet © 2026

    </footer>

</body>

</html>